race.comment: Very moderate even by Highweight standards. VEINS WITHIN ROCK (4) has had two starts and although safely held both have been in richer maidens. Has upside and this far easier. Gets chance. REEL CRYSTAL (9) has been tested over further but looks well placed this line-up. Not far from the winner over a mile latest in a richer maiden and on that figure would go close here. HELIOSON (6) is a gelding by The Autumn Sun making debut for a form yard. Very well educated with a host of trials and jump-outs, and wouldn't have to be special to feature here fresh. Watch the market closely. MISS WATTLEBANK (7) has been safely held at last couple but is drawn for a soft run on the inside. Gets chance to improve. EM ELL BEE (5) was fair fresh over a sprint journey but fitter and looks suited over the extra ground.
